{"tid":1996320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十年-浮瓜劇情：2020年五一勞動節當天，政府高層精心策畫一樁恐怖攻擊，企圖引起社會恐慌，加速中央推行國安法","createTime":"2020-05-01T01:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T01:50:07.000Z","uid":61282,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d527570f75089ca6a8324617c77d3598486c9f31","tid":1996320,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"片段採用黑白畫面拍攝。講述<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年五一勞動節慶活動期間</span>，一所中學的禮堂正舉行由建制派政黨舉辦的蛇齋餅糭活動。與此同時，樓上課室有多名政界高層、警隊以及黑社會，<span style=\"color: red;\">計劃射傷兩位建制派議員以製造混亂，激起港人恐懼，從而加速中央實施「國安法」。</span>兩名黑社會「炒散」獲分配「任務」，眼見可觀酬勞，決定孤注一擲執行任務，卻沒料想到最後被警方槍殺。這一連串的計劃目的只是在於令「國安法」成功通過。"},{"pid":"d5b1dfbb8ed3c952253dd6fe3c33ae56edeb735a","tid":1996320,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"百份已經預告晒今日會發生咩事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996286</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nCredit to #2 蕉直相對巴打"},{"pid":"11fa689587869a678983a4d57b346b37c834c3c7","tid":1996320,"uid":61282,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaVyGU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaVyGU2.jpg&h=74b2a3e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5789c906402774944f39748da9a7ee4dd76a72b","tid":1996320,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"李家超 ：可凍結疑犯資產！任何人阻礙警方對恐怖分子執法，同樣需要被處理！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1995609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1995609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bfb2f819b2a430b62fe9d437dd0c36ad00ca61ce","tid":1996320,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"東方：警方五一派出大批便衣警員埋伏多個商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}